title: Grateful Dead Live at Giants Stadium on 1993-06-06
description:
Set 1

Here Comes Sunshine, Minglewood Blues, Ramble On Rose, Broken Arrow, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Lazy River Road, Let It Grow

Set 2

Bertha-> Good Lovin'-> Uncle John's Band-> Playin' In The Band-> Drums-> Jam-> Corinna-> Attics Of My Life-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Liberty

Sting opened
